options.content:
#### RabbitMQ Queues

Queue details in cluster ${rabbitmq_cluster}, vhost: ${rabbitmq_vhost}, queue: ${queue} .

panels.description: Rate of new messages inserted into the queue.

targets.expr: sum by (rabbitmq_cluster, vhost, rabbitmq_node) (rate(rabbitmq_detailed_queue_exchange_messages_published_total{vhost="$rabbitmq_vhost", queue="${queue:raw}"}[30s])  * on(instance, job) group_left(rabbitmq_cluster, rabbitmq_node) rabbitmq_identity_info {rabbitmq_endpoint=~"detailed|", rabbitmq_cluster="$rabbitmq_cluster", namespace="$namespace"})

panels.title: Incoming message rate

panels.description:
- **Acknowledgment rate:** The frequency at which acknowledgments from consumers are received, allowing messages to be removed from the queue.
- **Auto-ack rate:** Messages removed from the queue without acknowledgment.

targets.expr: sum by (queue, rabbitmq_node) (irate(rabbitmq_detailed_queue_messages_acked_total{queue="${queue:raw}", vhost="$rabbitmq_vhost"}[30s])  * on(instance, job) group_left(rabbitmq_cluster, rabbitmq_node) rabbitmq_identity_info {rabbitmq_endpoint=~"detailed|", rabbitmq_cluster="$rabbitmq_cluster", namespace="$namespace"})

sum by (queue, rabbitmq_node) (irate(rabbitmq_detailed_queue_messages_delivered_total{queue="${queue:raw}", vhost="$rabbitmq_vhost"}[30s])  * on(instance, job) group_left(rabbitmq_cluster, rabbitmq_node) rabbitmq_identity_info {rabbitmq_endpoint=~"detailed|", rabbitmq_cluster="$rabbitmq_cluster", namespace="$namespace"})

panels.title: Acknowledgment and delivery rate

panels.description: The count of messages delivered to consumers that are pending acknowledgment before they can be removed from the queue.

targets.expr: rabbitmq_detailed_queue_messages_unacked{queue="${queue:raw}", vhost="$rabbitmq_vhost"}  * on(instance, job) group_left(rabbitmq_cluster, rabbitmq_node) rabbitmq_identity_info {rabbitmq_endpoint=~"detailed|", rabbitmq_cluster="$rabbitmq_cluster", namespace="$namespace"}

panels.title: Unacknowledged messages

panels.description: Number of channels publishing to this queue.

targets.expr: count by (rabbitmq_cluster, vhost, rabbitmq_node) (rate(rabbitmq_detailed_queue_exchange_messages_published_total{vhost="$rabbitmq_vhost", queue="${queue:raw}"}[30s])  * on(instance, job) group_left(rabbitmq_cluster, rabbitmq_node) rabbitmq_identity_info {rabbitmq_endpoint=~"detailed|", rabbitmq_cluster="$rabbitmq_cluster", namespace="$namespace"})

panels.title: Publisher count

panels.description: The total number of consumers subscribed to the queue.

targets.expr: rabbitmq_detailed_queue_consumers{queue="${queue:raw}", vhost="$rabbitmq_vhost"}  * on(instance, job) group_left(rabbitmq_cluster, rabbitmq_node) rabbitmq_identity_info {rabbitmq_endpoint=~"detailed|", rabbitmq_cluster="$rabbitmq_cluster", namespace="$namespace"}

panels.title: Consumer count

panels.description: Total number of messages in the queue, including unacknowledged messages. For best performance, queues should be empty.

targets.expr: rabbitmq_detailed_queue_messages{ vhost="$rabbitmq_vhost", queue="${queue:raw}"}  * on(instance, job) group_left(rabbitmq_cluster, rabbitmq_node) rabbitmq_identity_info {rabbitmq_endpoint=~"detailed|", rabbitmq_cluster="$rabbitmq_cluster", namespace="$namespace"}

panels.title: Queue length

panels.description:
Rate of client applications polling the queue for messages. 

The metrics shown are the following:

- **Queue Polling with Acknowledgment:** In this mode, the queue requires an acknowledgment from the client to confirm message processing before removing the message from the queue.
- **Queue Polling without Acknowledgment:** Messages are immediately removed from the queue once served, with no need for processing acknowledgment from the client.
- **Polling on Empty Queue:** This metric tracks the count of poll events when the queue is empty, indicating unnecessary polling activity.

targets.expr: sum by (queue, rabbitmq_node) (irate(rabbitmq_detailed_queue_get_ack_total{queue="${queue:raw}", vhost="$rabbitmq_vhost"}[30s])  * on(instance, job) group_left(rabbitmq_cluster, rabbitmq_node) rabbitmq_identity_info {rabbitmq_endpoint=~"detailed|", rabbitmq_cluster="$rabbitmq_cluster", namespace="$namespace"})

sum by (queue, rabbitmq_node) (irate(rabbitmq_detailed_queue_get_total{queue="${queue:raw}", vhost="$rabbitmq_vhost"}[30s])  * on(instance, job) group_left(rabbitmq_cluster, rabbitmq_node) rabbitmq_identity_info {rabbitmq_endpoint=~"detailed|", rabbitmq_cluster="$rabbitmq_cluster", namespace="$namespace"})

sum by (queue, rabbitmq_node) (irate(rabbitmq_detailed_queue_get_empty_total{queue="${queue:raw}", vhost="$rabbitmq_vhost"}[30s])  * on(instance, job) group_left(rabbitmq_cluster, rabbitmq_node) rabbitmq_identity_info {rabbitmq_endpoint=~"detailed|", rabbitmq_cluster="$rabbitmq_cluster", namespace="$namespace"})

panels.title: Message polling rates

list.definition: query_result(rabbitmq_detailed_queue_consumers  * on(instance, job) group_left(rabbitmq_cluster, rabbitmq_node) rabbitmq_identity_info {rabbitmq_endpoint=~"detailed|", rabbitmq_cluster="$rabbitmq_cluster"})
list.label: vhost
list.name: rabbitmq_vhost

query.query: query_result(rabbitmq_detailed_queue_consumers  * on(instance, job) group_left(rabbitmq_cluster, rabbitmq_node) rabbitmq_identity_info {rabbitmq_endpoint=~"detailed|", rabbitmq_cluster="$rabbitmq_cluster"})
